

* Select models to run
Let models = ['IGC033S101_L1', 'IGC025S08S1_L1']

** References to components using the models
Let refs = ['Q5', 'Q1']


foreach model models


	** Set component value
	foreach ref refs
		Let SetComponentValue(ref & '.value', model)
	next

	** Create netlist
	Netlist design.net

	Echo {'Running simulation using ' & model}
	** Run simulation
	run design.net


next
